						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">rainwarrior wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">when importing, make sure ZP variables use <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">.zpimport</tt> instead of <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">.import</tt>.</div><br />In ca65 the former is <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">.importzp</tt>.</div>

